BT 1 0 0 1 0 51 Tm 12 TL /F1 9 Tf 0 0 0 rg (The corpus interpreted this as chaotic. It is not. The recovery at delay=80 and delay=200 are ) Tj /F2 9 Tf (quantum Poincare) Tj T* (recurrences) Tj /F1 9 Tf ( -- a well-known phenomenon in finite-dimensional quantum systems \(Bocchieri & Loinger 1957\) where the) Tj T* (state returns arbitrarily close to its initial state for sufficiently long times. The revival at delay=80 ~= 4x the collapse time) Tj T* (\(~20\) and delay=200 ~= 10x suggest the detuning frequency and system frequency have an approximate 2:5 rational ratio,) Tj T* (creating structured quantum revivals.) Tj T* ET
